#: ''The verbs in sentences like "Do it!" and "Say what you like!" are in the '''imperative'''.''
# {{lb|en|countable|grammar}} A [[verb]] in imperative mood.
# {{lb|en|countable}} An essential action, a [[must]]: something which is imperative.
